title: Veronica Mars S04E00 - Season 4 Presentation (FBI Pilot) DVDRip
description:
Before Veronica Mars got canceled, creator Rob Thomas was given the opportunity to try fast forwarding the series several years.

This 12 minute pilot shows Veronica starting her new career at the FBI.
Like it or hate it, it's what a Season 4 would have looked like (Grey's FBI Agents Featuring Veronica Mars).
